<div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-snippet wprm-recipe-template-nates-jump-to-button"><a href="#recipe" data-recipe="16019" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #173b61;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-jump wprm-recipe-link wprm-jump-to-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-jump-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-jump-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g class="nc-icon-wrapper" fill="#ffffff"><path data-color="color-2" d="M9,2h6c0.6,0,1-0.4,1-1s-0.4-1-1-1H9C8.4,0,8,0.4,8,1S8.4,2,9,2z"></path> <path fill="#ffffff" d="M16,11V5c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1H9C8.4,4,8,4.4,8,5v6H1.9L12,23.6L22.1,11H16z"></path></g></svg></span> Jump to Recipe</a>

<a href="#recipe-video" data-recipe="16019" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #173b61;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-jump-video wprm-recipe-link wprm-jump-to-video-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-jump-video-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-jump-video-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g class="nc-icon-wrapper" fill="#ffffff"><path fill="#ffffff" d="M22,8H2C1.448,8,1,8.447,1,9v14c0,0.553,0.448,1,1,1h20c0.552,0,1-0.447,1-1V9C23,8.447,22.552,8,22,8z M9,20v-8l7,4L9,20z"></path> <rect data-color="color-2" x="0.001" y="2.111" transform="matrix(0.9798 -0.1999 0.1999 0.9798 -0.4028 2.2323)" width="21.701" height="2"></rect></g></svg></span> Jump to Video</a></div>
<p>We love elk meat, and a new recipe I&#8217;ve been making regularly is <strong>elk steak stroganoff</strong>. This recipe is super easy to make and the elk steak meat is so tender.</p>



<p>Not to mention the rich incredible flavors of the creamy mushroom sauce we make for this stroganoff recipe is second to none.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><picture><source srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3.webp 800w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3-200x300.webp 200w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3-683x1024.webp 683w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3-768x1152.webp 768w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3-150x225.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" type="image/webp"><img data-no-lazy="" fetchpriority="high" src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3.jpg" height="1200" width="800" srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3.jpg 800w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-3-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" class="wp-image-15889 sp-no-webp" alt="Creamy mushroom sauce and elk steak overtop of egg noodles on a white plate that&#039;s sitting on a blue and white place setting. " decoding="async" data-pin-description="We love elk meat and a new recipe I&#039;ve been making is elk steak stroganoff. It&#039;s rich in flavor and the elk meat is tender, covered in a creamy mushroom sauce, creating a hearty and satisfying meal."  > </picture></figure>



