<p></p>
<!-- [/element-20892] -->



<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> In the same skillet, saute onions in butter until soft, then add mushrooms and cook until browned.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><picture><source data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3.webp 1200w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-300x200.webp 300w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-1024x683.webp 1024w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-768x512.webp 768w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-150x100.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" type="image/webp"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" height="800" width="1200" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3.jpg 1200w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-150x100.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" class="wp-image-15892 sp-no-webp" alt="Sauteing onions in a cast iron skillet. " decoding="async" data-pin-description="We love elk meat and a new recipe I&#039;ve been making is elk steak stroganoff. It&#039;s rich in flavor and the elk meat is tender, covered in a creamy mushroom sauce, creating a hearty and satisfying meal."  data-lazy-src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3.jpg" ><noscript><img src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3.jpg" height="800" width="1200" srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3.jpg 1200w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-3-150x100.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" class="wp-image-15892 sp-no-webp" alt="Sauteing onions in a cast iron skillet. " decoding="async" data-pin-description="We love elk meat and a new recipe I&#039;ve been making is elk steak stroganoff. It&#039;s rich in flavor and the elk meat is tender, covered in a creamy mushroom sauce, creating a hearty and satisfying meal."  ></noscript> </picture></figure>



<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Stir in flour until it&#8217;s well incorporated.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><picture><source data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-1024x683.jpg 1024w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-300x200.webp 300w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-768x512.webp 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-150x100.jpg 150w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe.webp 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" type="image/webp"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20683'%3E%3C/svg%3E" height="683" width="1024" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-150x100.jpg 150w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe.jpg 1200w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" class="wp-image-15893 sp-no-webp" alt="Adding in flour to the sauteed onions." decoding="async"  data-lazy-src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-1024x683.jpg" ><noscript><img src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-1024x683.jpg" height="683" width="1024" srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-150x100.jpg 150w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" class="wp-image-15893 sp-no-webp" alt="Adding in flour to the sauteed onions." decoding="async"  ></noscript> </picture></figure>



<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Finally, add beef broth, heavy cream, and Dijon mustard. Mix well. Return elk strips to the skillet, bring to a simmer, then reduce heat to thicken the sauce and finish cooking meat—salt and pepper to taste.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><picture><source data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2.webp 1200w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-300x200.webp 300w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-1024x683.webp 1024w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-768x512.webp 768w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-150x100.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" type="image/webp"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" height="800" width="1200" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2.jpg 1200w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-150x100.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" class="wp-image-15891 sp-no-webp" alt="Adding beef broth to the cast iron skillet." decoding="async" data-id="15891" data-pin-description="We love elk meat and a new recipe I&#039;ve been making is elk steak stroganoff. It&#039;s rich in flavor and the elk meat is tender, covered in a creamy mushroom sauce, creating a hearty and satisfying meal."  data-lazy-src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2.jpg" ><noscript><img src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2.jpg" height="800" width="1200" srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2.jpg 1200w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-recipe-2-150x100.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" class="wp-image-15891 sp-no-webp" alt="Adding beef broth to the cast iron skillet." decoding="async" data-id="15891" data-pin-description="We love elk meat and a new recipe I&#039;ve been making is elk steak stroganoff. It&#039;s rich in flavor and the elk meat is tender, covered in a creamy mushroom sauce, creating a hearty and satisfying meal."  ></noscript> </picture></figure>
</figure>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="serve-enjoy">Serve &amp; Enjoy</h3>



<p>Serve the creamy elk stroganoff over cooked egg noodles.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><picture><source data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2.webp 1200w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-300x200.webp 300w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-1024x683.webp 1024w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-768x512.webp 768w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-150x100.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" type="image/webp"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" height="800" width="1200" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2.jpg 1200w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-150x100.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" class="wp-image-15888 sp-no-webp" alt="Elk stroganoff on a serving plate with egg noodles. " decoding="async" data-pin-description="We love elk meat and a new recipe I&#039;ve been making is elk steak stroganoff. It&#039;s rich in flavor and the elk meat is tender, covered in a creamy mushroom sauce, creating a hearty and satisfying meal."  data-lazy-src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2.jpg" ><noscript><img src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2.jpg" height="800" width="1200" srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2.jpg 1200w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-150x100.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" class="wp-image-15888 sp-no-webp" alt="Elk stroganoff on a serving plate with egg noodles. " decoding="async" data-pin-description="We love elk meat and a new recipe I&#039;ve been making is elk steak stroganoff. It&#039;s rich in flavor and the elk meat is tender, covered in a creamy mushroom sauce, creating a hearty and satisfying meal."  ></noscript> </picture></figure>



