<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="cooking-tips"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Cooking_tips"></span>Cooking tips<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>For the best flavor, make sure the internal temperature reaches 130°F for medium-rare doneness. </li>



<li>Use high-heat oils to prevent smoking during searing. </li>



<li>Cut the steaks into strips against the grain to make the steaks more tender and easier to chew.</li>



<li>Stir often to prevent the ingredients from sticking to the bottom of the pan.</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="serving-suggestions"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Serving_suggestions"></span>Serving suggestions<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<p>While the popular choice is to use egg noodles, fettuccine&nbsp;noodles are just as good. You can also serve this dish over <a href="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/how-to-parboil-rice/">rice</a>. This completes and makes a perfect and satisfying meal.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-the-best-pan-to-use"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="What_is_the_best_pan_to_use"></span>What is the best pan to use?<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<p>I like using a cast iron skillet because it distributes heat evenly and retains heat well, ensuring consistent cooking throughout and keeping the sauce warm. </p>



<p>Just be sure to use a 12-inch skillet or larger so you have room for all the delicious ingredients.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="can-i-still-make-this-recipe-if-i-dont-have-elk-steak"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Can_I_still_make_this_recipe_if_I_dont_have_elk_steak"></span>Can I still make this recipe if I don&#8217;t have elk steak?<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Yes, if you don&#8217;</span>t have elk meat, you can use <a href="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/cook-venison-steak/">venison steak</a> or any beef, such as a <a href="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/flat-iron-steak/">beef flat iron steak</a>, or sirloin, as I do in my <a href="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/dutch-oven-beef-stroganoff/">dutch oven beef stroganoff</a>. I also have made a <a href="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/venison-stroganoff/">venison stroganoff</a> using ground venison, which can be substituted for ground elk.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><picture><source data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4.webp 800w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-200x300.webp 200w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-683x1024.webp 683w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-768x1152.webp 768w,https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-150x225.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" type="image/webp"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20800%201200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" height="1200" width="800" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4.jpg 800w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-150x225.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" class="wp-image-15890 sp-no-webp" alt="Creamy sauce over elk steak on top of noodles." decoding="async" data-pin-description="We love elk meat and a new recipe I&#039;ve been making is elk steak stroganoff. It&#039;s rich in flavor and the elk meat is tender, covered in a creamy mushroom sauce, creating a hearty and satisfying meal."  data-lazy-src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4.jpg" ><noscript><img src="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4.jpg" height="1200" width="800" srcset="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4.jpg 800w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-4-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" class="wp-image-15890 sp-no-webp" alt="Creamy sauce over elk steak on top of noodles." decoding="async" data-pin-description="We love elk meat and a new recipe I&#039;ve been making is elk steak stroganoff. It&#039;s rich in flavor and the elk meat is tender, covered in a creamy mushroom sauce, creating a hearty and satisfying meal."  ></noscript> </picture></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="i-hope-you-enjoy-elk-steak-stroganoff"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="I_hope_you_enjoy_Elk_Steak_Stroganoff"></span>I hope you enjoy Elk Steak Stroganoff.<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<p>This recipe is a family favorite that&#8217;s frequently requested. It has proven to be a hit with kids, so it is safe to say that it&#8217;s kid-approved. </p>



<p>Elk steak stroganoff makes a delicious dinner and is also perfect for meal prepping because it can be stored for 3-4 days in a sealed container in the fridge. </p>



<p>If you enjoyed this recipe, feel free to leave a comment below. Follow us on our social media platforms, Pinterest and Instagram @castironskilletcooking to stay connected.</p>



