nskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/elk-steak-stroganoff-2-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" class="sp-no-webp attachment-250x250 size-250x250 sp-no-webp" alt=""  ></noscript> </picture></div>
