<h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Elk_Steak_Stroganoff"></span>Elk Steak Stroganoff<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
<span class="wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-author wprm-block-text-light"><a href="https://www.castironskilletcooking.com/about/" target="_self">Laura Ascher</a></span>
<div class="wprm-spacer" style="height: 2px;"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">Homemade elk steak stroganoff with a creamy mushroom sauce.</span></div>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
